":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef6cd756f7e806d384a838d718f9eed022538912","tid":624172,"uid":24064,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"cec0c19c517d2887eae7f69dc69877712ff6145c","tid":624172,"uid":90946,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T17:14:26.000Z","msg":"其實in house同agency  係咩<br />\n成日見人講但唔知係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係某類型design 先有？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T17:48:07.000Z","msg":"簡單講：<br />\nIn house :公司內部設計，即係黎黎去去都幫自己公司做宣傳，產品等等<br />\nAgency:公司接客做，你係幫客人做設計，幫客做宣傳同產品等等，公司個角色有d 似中介，呢類公司最仆街，佢會就哂個客玩狗死班designer,無所不用其極，3日工作量會同客講即日攪點然後迫你ot死出黎，佢只會理客感受，只要客人想ge佢都會應承，絕對係練工勝地，燃燒生命ge地獄，我敢講你做1年可以有對等於in-house 2年以上ge 經驗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T00:02:00.000Z","msg":"唔該曬你嘅解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁應該我果類型唔係<br />\nInterior 都無分而d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T03:24:59.000Z","msg":"Interior應該算Agency, 除非你公司自己起完樓裝修黎賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da01c0bc6688da0f40807862957404db69b63ecd","tid":624172,"uid":24064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"643a6ee13ac20d7ad36ae6e64c3e9f55563ac606","tid":624172,"uid":64318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27a37a4f634c4d2098124372ab9884437940b40c","tid":624172,"uid":24064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"415eae1272ee3fa2b1349c805422e7b1acb852c9","tid":624172,"uid":165925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T15:49:51.000Z","msg":"［s]1年full time designer亂入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n清讀design出身？<br />\n有冇讀master? <br />\n仲有冇熱誠？<br />\n係咪仲好中意靚野？<br />\n[/s]"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T17:39:04.000Z","msg":"有design相關ge high dip同top up degree<br />\n無master<br />\n熱誠仲有ge, 我諗正確黎講係見到醜嘢會頂唔順，有強迫症咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T02:01:55.000Z",